istent guest delight; Revenue is guided by informed market insight and strategic positioning; and Returns are strengthened through disciplined operations and responsible financial stewardship.\nRepair & Maintenance forms the backbone of asset integrity and brand presentation, ensuring the product remains timeless, well-kept, and aligned with guest expectations.\nA culture shaped by Respect and sustained through Recognition empowered teams to perform with pride, purpose, and a genuine commitment to exceptional service—creating environments where guests feel appreciated and employees feel valued.", "addressCountryOnly": "Thailand", "addressWithCountry": "Bangkok City, Thailand", "addressWithoutCountry": "Bangkok City", "backgroundPic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5616AQH4B4UL4N2-pg/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/0/1621607572090?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=P3dL_oVK8Hypa0AKm3nN1jChyDAefNrXzy-EEGzW0BU", "companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "companyLinkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/frasershospitality/", "companyName": "Frasers Hospitality", "companySize": "5001-10000", "companyWebsite": "https://www.frasersproperty.com/hospitality", "connections": "6246", "creatorWebsite/0/category": "PORTFOLIO", "creatorWebsite/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/redir/suspicious-page?url=sumant-singh%2elovable%2eapp", "currentJobDuration": "1 yr 10 mos", "currentJobDurationInYrs": "1.83", "educations/0/companyId": "20326", "educations/0/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/school/indira-gandhi-national-open-university/", "educations/0/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:20326", "educations/0/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4D0BAQFSeGt81F28yg/company-logo_200_200/company-logo_200_200/0/1631325920062?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=V8dYg1lymTz4mhXvaFvsveBVUpyVsYzqCOF6vdLjI5c", "educations/0/period/endedOn/month": "1", "educations/0/period/endedOn/year": "2024", "educations/0/period/startedOn/month": "1", "educa