ds of the hotel and meet or exceed customer expectations.\n•\tActively and regularly interacts with guests, associates and colleagues, not limited to current and potential clients, owning company representatives, suppliers, competitors and other members of the local community.\n•\tAssist with preparation of the hotel’s annual budget and more specifically monitors and controls the budgets of the Rooms Division, S&R and F&B, Kitchen Departments.\n•\tParticipates in the preparation of the annual business plan.\n•\tCo-ordinates with the Sales & Marketing Department for the preparation and implementation of promotions regarding guest rooms and F&B.\n•\tManage all social media aspects for the resort.\n•\tOversee all health and safety, fire and emergency procedures.\n•\tPerforms in the capacity of the General Manager in his absence\n\nLocated between a tropical lagoon and the sparkling waters of the Andaman Sea, Outrigger Laguna Phuket Beach Resort features a wide range of accommodation with modern interiors with contemporary Thai touches. For guests seeking a more personalised experience, the resort boasts a dedicated club concept including club rooms and an executive club lounge.", "experiences/1/jobEndedOn": "8-2021", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Outrigger Laguna Phuket Beach Resort", "experiences/1/jobLocationCountry": "US", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "7-2015", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/1/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C560BAQHwEdQr58A8JQ/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1671055172829/outrigger_hospitality_group_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=JXz95Iv3bU79rYjxHc7omlHmcVs3rJkGn3ZK-N5D1gQ", "experiences/1/title": "Resort Manager", "experiences/2/companyId": "49977", "experiences/2/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/2/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/outrigger-hospitality-group/", "experiences/2/companyName": "Outrigger Hospitality Group", "experiences/2/companySize": "1001-5000", "experiences/2/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:49977", "experiences/2/companyWebsite": "http://www.outrigger.com", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "4.5 star resort incorporating 353 apartments, hotel rooms and suites with one restaurant outsourced.\n\nResponsibilities\n•\tManage the hotel operation and provide effective leadership across every department using both a hands on and strategic approach for 356 rooms.\n•\tExecute administrative responsibilities\n•\tIn charge of all hotel operating departments\n•\tRanked Number one position on TripAdvisor for the destination.\n•\tManage the operation of 353 hotel rooms and apartments in two complexes under the terms and conditions of the caretaker’s agreement\n•\tOwner Relations (residents and investors)\n•\tLiving on site with 24 hour accessibility. \n\nOutrigger Twin Towns Resort is an expansive Coolangatta beach resort offering fully self contained one, two and three bedroom apartment holiday accommodation and stylishly appointed hotel rooms across the Ocean and Harbour Towers. All accommodation features private balconies with many offering sensational views overlooking the beaches of the Southern Gold Coast, the sparkling blue waters of the Tweed River, and the picturesque hinterland. The resort features two pools, spas, two tennis courts, mini golf, games room, gymnasium with steam room, outdoor barbeque areas and undercover car parking. \n\nTwin Towns Service Club adds a world of entertainment in the same complex. The state-of-the-art conference facility, show stages, slot machines and Twin Towns' famous showroom are accessible to all resort guests. Twin Towns Service Club operates a variety of restaurant, servery and bar facilities; Club staff looking after resort guests with breakfast in Signatures Restaurant and a Sundowners in the Lobby Bar.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "7-2015", "experiences/2/jobLocationCountry": "US", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "7-2012", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/logo"