din.com/in/mihajlo-stracenski-17742536/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAeJlKsBWku4HMfuORfqIETxcZJYWky3VS0", "recommendations/2/context": "Stephen was David's client", "recommendations/2/date": "January 14, 2021", "recommendations/2/description": "David is one of the top PGA Professional ambassadors that I know. His trick shows are unique & tailored specifically towards your business needs, great value, highly engaging and brilliant entertainment around, simply a must have for your golf event. A true gentleman with a passion for promoting the game of golf. Watch out for the amazing Edwards Scissor hands ! ", "recommendations/2/name": "David Edwards", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "PGA Golf Professional & Honorary Member of PGA / Golf Trick Shows at David Edwards Golf Trick Show", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidedwardsgolfshow/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAARMWZ8Bsbzx7KYxZA6HM5Mlfumyj8sixc8", "recommendations/3/context": "Stephen worked with Cuong on the same team", "recommendations/3/date": "November 23, 2019", "recommendations/3/description": "Cuong is a unique individual with a luxury collection back ground, highly personable, culturally-astute and exceptional in his chosen field of F&B. One trait I see with Cuong is that he has exceptional leadership and entrepreneurial skills that will one day see him as a GM and/or leader of an international organisation.", "recommendations/3/name": "Cuong V.", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Luxury Hospitality | Business Development | Real Estate | Project Management", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cuong-v-1a5b9a46/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAnJQY0BUOPLhOQy8UYFShhOHSeUYe2Xf0Q", "recommendations/4/context": "Stephen worked with Wesley on the same team", "recommendations/4/date": "July 29, 2018", "recommendations/4/description": "Wesley is simply an outstanding hospitality professional within the discipline of F&B. \n\nHe has an extremely bright and prosperous future ahead of him within the luxury collection and is key to his current work place.\n\nOne of Wesley’s many traits that I’ve become accustomed to is that he is extremely personable, whilst being an absolute pleasure to work alongside with. ", "recommendations/4/name": "Wesley Hepburn", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Assistant Director Food and Beverage at The Ritz-Carlton Hotel Company, L.L.C.", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/wesley-hepburn-3b2b064a/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAp8jrYBBvBwWCvAYb7yxuxxZhpVSjnrosM", "recommendations/5/context": "Victor was senior to Stephen but didn't manage Stephen directly", "recommendations/5/date": "January 10, 2017", "recommendations/5/description": "It is not often that you come across 'the ultimate hospitality professional' - Victor is just all of that and so much more. His attitude and demeanour is one that appeals to all that are in his training programs, instantly likeable, endless real-life examples that fire the messages clearly home (and are remembered), combined with a dry and professional sense of humour, all at a hospitality level that is nothing short of 'par excellence'. One of Victor's many traits was the way that as my superior he just 'got stuck in' when we were understaffed in a recent golf event in Bali, connecting with all levels of staffs, taking instructions and direction to simply 'get the job done' ensuring success was high on the agenda. Passion, enthusiasm, immaculate appearance combined with outstanding knowledge are just some descriptions of his many talents. Looking for a Director of Learning for your property? Then Victor has my highest of recommendations one can offer.", "recommendations/5/name": "Victor Lau (IHRP - SP)", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Head, Global Learning & Development and Talent Management at Millennium Hotels and Resorts", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-lau-ihrp-sp-a334681b/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQpQccBL7pJzUcCnbLBS-kyQQNknIK8rzs", "recommendations/6/context": "Stephen worked with Ahmed Alaa on the same team", "recommendations/6/date": "April 7, 2014", "recommendations/6/description": "Ahmed is a professional in his own right, a man of 'stand up character' and by all means a natural born leader. I had the pleasure of working with Ahmed in Palma de Mallorca in 2012 for an exclusive golf event/ wedding  which was nothing short of first-class. I highly recommend Ahmed.", "recommendations/6/name": "Ahmed Alaa Darwish", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "F&B Marketing Specialist, Radio Host & Podcaster", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/aadarwish/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKBdS4BQsDm6RLl6HYnrIsG7aiFoE2miU8", "recommendations/7/context": "Stephen worked with Dean on the same team", "recommendations/7/date": "August 7, 2012", "recommendations/7/description": "I have personally known Dean since I joined Puttenham Golf Club as a PGA Trainee back in the year 2000. Dean is a PGA Golf Professional of the highest calibre in every sense, an exceptional player of the game, and a first class golf coach with the patience of a saint!\n\nOne thing that struck me as Dean personally took me under his wing to mentor me through my PGA Training was his commitment to the 'task in hand' of dealing with every single aspect and more that the PGA required for him to do as a PGA Approved training establishment, which often involved above and beyond his role and responsibilities for the club. 18 years at Puttenham Golf Club just illustrates Dean's dedication not only to the club, but to himself as one of Surrey's finest PGA Golf Professionals that thrives on perfection, honesty and integrity. \n\nPuttenham Golf Club is very lucky to have secured the services of Dean Lintott, as I wouldn't be where I am today without his professionalism.", "recommendations/7/name": "Dean Lintott", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Head Golf Professional at Puttenham Golf Club", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dean-lintott-07331756/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAvLBJcBJSwm1Tn1fzYcl4h_hT4UL5NczyY", "recommendations/8/context": "Stephen worked with Stephen but they were at different companies", "recommendations/8/date": "June 4, 2012", "recommendations/8/description": "I have had the pleasure of personally working with Stephen since 1995 when he was a very active member of the golf club that I managed in Saudi Arabia; at that time he was quickly building his successful career within PMI. One of Stephen's finest qualities is as a top shelf 'seasoned marketing specialist' who simply knows his business inside out. Other qualities include being a very personable gentleman. In relation to the golf, his approach was constantly ensuring his brand got maximum exposure to each and every member of the club, by devising new and innovative marketing ideas via first class corporate golf tournaments, that constantly attracted a full field. Stephen is also a very proficient golfer.", "recommendations/8/name": "Stephen Cleary", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Consultant I Chief Marketing Officer | Brand Strategy | Digital Transformation | Marketing Strategies | Customer Insights & Experience", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephen-cleary-25aa164/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADcsuYBHrPmbIhv9Wd7-tYydg1XenmIFSE", "recommendations/9/context": "Stephen was senior to Nelson but didn't manage Nelson directly", "recommendations/9/date": "July 20, 2011", "recommendations/9/description": "Sea Links City recently held the MercedesTrophy Final 2011, the largest and most prestigious amateur golf event in Vietnam. Nelson played a pivotal role as Director of F&B for the event catering for no less than 2 Gala Dinners of 280 pax to the highest international standards. His creativity and imagination is second to none & the Sea Links Beach Hotel is very fortunate to have secured his services. On a personal note Nelson is very calming and has a very positive 'can do attitude' that I find very pleasing, - I am sure he has a very bright future ahead of him.", "recommendations/9/name": "Nelson Yap", "recommendations/9/subtitle": "Regional Sales Manager at Trutec Pte Ltd", "recommendations/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nelson-yap-10b5ba4/", "recommendations/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADM-xsBKp95TQcu6GLnDOVXYTXXgO0JSU4", "recommendations/10/context": "Stephen managed Sunny directly", "recommendations/10/date": "July 14, 2011", "recommendations/10/description": "Ms Kim Jihai is currently employed as my DOSM at Sea Links Golf & CC in Mui Ne, Vietnam and has also successfully worked in the 5-Star Sea Links Beach Hotel. Ms Kim has been instrumental in the recent success of Sea Links Golf in significantly reducing complaints, developing business contacts and is the driving force behind all Sales & Marketing at the club. \n\nMs Kim was heavily involved in securing two of the most prestigious events of the year in Vietnam, The MercedesTrophy Final & The Guide Awards. A professional hotelier by trade, fluent both spoken & written in French, Korean & English are just some of her language skills. On a personal basis she is liked by all persons who come into contact with her. On a professional basis Ms Kim is a natural born leader who has quickly learned the golf industry business therefore has a bright future in the hospitality/ golf business.", "recommendations/10/name": "Sunny Kim", "recommendations/10/subtitle": "Global Sales | Hospitality Management Professional |", "recommendations/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sunny-kim-41881736/", "recommendations/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAeYgpQBtOq972VBUSPKG8L3g9evl7NzXCI", "recommendations/11/context": "Stephen worked with Mark but they were at different companies", "recommendations/11/date": "January 26, 2011", "recommendations/11/description": "Mark is one of life's unique entrepreneurs, on a personal basis he is one of life's true friends, and is the 1st person that I call if I want to play a relaxing 9 holes. \n\nI first had the opportunity to work with Mark during the Mercedes Trophy back in 2006, of which his management skills and vision were instrumental to the success that the brand has been driven to in Vietnam to-date. Mark's work ethic is outstanding and its a real credit to how golf and Mercedes Benz Vietnam has developed over the past 5 years or so as the leading amateur golf tournament across the country. \n\nIf you have got an idea, a plan for a new concept and you need a professional set of ears to listen and develop it, then simply give him a call, I personally recommend him.", "recommendations/11/name": "Mark Khan", "recommendations/11/subtitle": "Supporting the growth ambitions of local and global companies", "recommendations/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/markkhanvietnambusinessdevelopmentconsultant/", "recommendations/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEiWOkB43g8-_e5GQkFytrpqiHqpPHDrVI", "recommendations/12/context": "Stephen worked with John P. but they were at different companies", "recommendations/12/date": "April 13, 2010", "recommendations/12/description": "First and foremost John is one of the most genuine persons that I have ever been fortunate enough to have worked with, as well as become a good friend of. Whilst working for the Intercontinental Bali, John headed the F&B Division that provided all the hospitality catering during the 2009 EJ Indonesia Open at New Kuta Golf & Ocean View in Bali. \n\nHis service, professionalism and outstanding work ethics allows him to deliver a first class service, each-day and every-day, combined with his passion for 6 star hospitality and very likeble personality, are traits that enable him to be a very sought after individual. Outside of work John is a devoted family man with strong values and principles.\n\nIf ever I want to play a round of golf either for business or pleasure, John Rees would definitely be my first choice as a partner!", "recommendations/12/name": "John P. Rees ", "recommendations/12/subtitle": "Senior Vice President Hotel Operations Hard Rock International Passionate Hospitality Professional, Global Citizen, Restless Adventurer, Committed family supporter and ultimate disrupter", "recommendations/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/john-p-rees-40a3702/", "recommendations/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABovUoBRQVOOVbtow4BPF_HnQZGF7xOnn4", "recommendations/13/context": "Stephen worked with Vincent but they were at different companies", "recommendations/13/date": "March 25, 2010", "recommendations/13/description": "Vincent Brian Wong is a professional of the highest calibre in the field of event management. I first met Vincent in October 2008 where I was the General Manager of New Kuta Golf & Ocean View, in Bali, Indonesia. Vincent was the Event Manager for GlobalOne, who were the  management group for Indonesia's largest sporting event of 2009, \n'The Enjoy Jakarta Indonesia Open'.\n\nOn first meeting with Vincent I found him to instantly like-able, not only by myself and all the New Kuta Golf staff, but by all who came into contact with him. This was evident as I watched on a daily basis his role unfold, he received the utmost amount of respect from his team of 50+ peers along with both the Asian & European Tour Directors. Throughout the entire project he displayed nothing short of 'first-class' qualities, to the extent which has earned him his role that he performs to-date.\n\nVincent is a man of his word, he is a very high achiever with copious quantities of integrity, and most of all a very approachable and competent team player/ manager. One of my most memorable traits when working with Vincent was his demeanor of that 'His door was always wide open for anyone, at anytime' and no matter how late I worked that night, whether it be until 2am or later, Vincent was still hard at it working away with a proud and genuine smile on his face!.\n\nFinally, Vincent was instrumental in the success of the 5th Indonesia Open that was held at New Kuta Golf & Ocean View. My endorsements do not come likely and it is with these brief words that I fully recommend Vincent Brian Wong as your International Golf Event Manager.", "recommendations/13/name": "Vincent Brian Wong", "recommendations/13/subtitle": "Consultant at vbw Marketing", "recommendations/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-brian-wong-99415217/", "recommendations/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANnJAAB923Y-v6oMpJFZsVoXUTQoQDVudo", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Victor was senior to Stephen but didn't manage Stephen directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "June 6, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Stephen is a visionary Leader who is very responsible, highly effective, committed and a hands on professional. He has vast experience in both sports and golf club management (both pre-opening and existing clubs).  As a professional sportsman, Stephen has also displayed great passion and competency in club management and all areas under his care.  Always producing great ideas and result oriented, he is also known as a friendly Leader who practice open door policy.\n\nI would not hesitate to recommend Stephen.   A leader with great personality, who is quick in his thinking, willing to roll up his sleeves, checking all corners of the golf course in good functional condition, meeting and knowing all the guest and club members in details (Sales & Marketing Skill etc) .  Stephen is definitely an asset to any establishment.  ", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Victor Lau (IHRP - SP)", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Head, Global Learning & Development and Talent Management at Millennium Hotels and Resorts", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-lau-ihrp-sp-a334681b/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQpQccBL7pJzUcCnbLBS-kyQQNknIK8rzs", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Robert was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "May 7, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Stephen is simply a great Golf Club Manager. Even if you are simply a social golfer like me, he always treats you a  personal warmth and respect. He cares about golf and  he cares that his guests get the most enjoyment out of their golf day. His professionalism is infectious...the people who work with him also work to his high standards because they follow his example. I am proud to recommend him.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Robert Mellor", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Local Governance, Planning and Capacity-Building Advisor", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-mellor-4139093b/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAh_2w8BNh4PglwqM_KF5RJixFmWy8Jv4ik", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Matteo was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "September 23, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Stephen Banks is one of the few people I've ever met who took his job seriously and devotedly. Since he arrived at Makadi Golf Course there was a huge and positive revolution compared to the management before. Organization, availability, professionalism just to list some of them. I personally took 2 memberships for me and my son for the first time since the beginning of this year but I feel like I have been member here all my life.\nI am very glad that a person like him could really change a place so much making it definitely worth going.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Matteo Minellono", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "UNIMIDI", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/minellono/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAINEoAB9xcJyjIM_Oka9S9rEBpyX_uMNXs", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Leif was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "September 2, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Stephen made a great job in building and managing the new Lakowe Golf & Country Estate in Lagos, which from the very start up was under the management of IMG. Under conditions which are very different from for example European standard and with less understanding of good quality golf, he achieved fantastic results in getting everything to work like any international golf club, high above ordinary Nigerian standard. He is also a very pleasant person, also skilled in selling and getting members to join and  enjoy the club. I can without any hesitation recommend Stephen to take on any Golf Management job, whether an old club in need for change and upgrade or a new club with a need to attract new members and get it to work and become a pleasant place for their golfing. As a person he is very easygoing but the same time, knows what he wants to achieve and can be very tough and driving in order to get his staff to reach the set targets and still keep the good spirit.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Leif Mattsson", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Senior Management Consultant at L exec management", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/leif-mattsson-a8ba487/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFmaAsBXxFAr2Qzt47U9h5US3xAAT0TpsA", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Eric was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "October 21, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "First of October 2013 Stephen organized the first anniversary of Lakowe Lakes the golf club that he manages at Lekki in Lagos Nigeria. From the reception of the players to the ceremony of the price giving the organization was flawless and should become a benchmark in Nigeria. Any company that would like to sponsor an event of golf in the country should come and see Stephen. He has authority even on the elements as, this day, the rain stopped after some holes for the good of everybody. He demonstrates the true professionalism, the one which is perceived when everything is achieved and well done. Part of this is his quality as \"maître de maison\" that makes him know how to welcome and entertain his guests. Trust him if you expect to spend some good moments in his environment.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Eric Maydieu", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Founder of EMC chez EMC", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-maydieu-8a0bab29/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAYMzTgBCdn0UsgVZyQ7EOgtNK3Sm5i4Kis", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Rick worked with Stephen but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "September 1, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Stephen is a dedicated and very knowledgable professional, he has a very strong marketing edge and has successfully increased revenues and service standards at the Clubs he has worked with. Innovation, enthusiasm, and dedication would be key words to describe his attributes.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Rick Blackie", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "General Manager at Sutera Harbour Marina Golf & Country Club", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rick-blackie-3391051/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAxf50BQzQ9n3IaMKG_6PQNraugxcoezRI", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Stephen was senior to Nelson but didn't manage Nelson directly", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "July 20, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "Stephen is an fast actions person with vision and full of inspiration, he have high expectations in his Golf teams and always lead by example, hands on yet justified to all his staffs and colleagues as well.A guy with character and his personal style of its own.I really enjoyed corporate working with him to make each events a success and fruitful return.", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Nelson Yap", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Regional Sales Manager at Trutec Pte Ltd", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nelson-yap-10b5ba4/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADM-xsBKp95TQcu6GLnDOVXYTXXgO0JSU4", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Brett was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "June 21, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "I have known Stephen for a short time since working on a project in Vietnam. In that time Stephen has been nothing but professional with a desire to ensure a mutual benefit for both businesses. His has an ability to build a relationship that is very business orientated but in a way that makes you feel like a close friend. This attribute is very rare in people of todays society and it is this attribute that will ensure he is succesful in his chosen career path. I wish Stephen every success and look forward to working with him on future projects.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Brett Wilson", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Area General Manager Phuket & Krabi at Accor", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/brett-wilson-b093031b/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQjbnkBEwTtCDyfhqehPYIfdXQxl0Gx_LM", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Stephen was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "August 25, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "I had the pleasure of work with Stephen in planning and organising several key events over a number of years in Saudi Arabia on behalf of Philip Morris (Marlboro). I always found Stephen to be the consummate professional. He is extremely hard working, passionate and committed to achieving excellent results on behalf of his clients. Stephen has a very positive \"can do\" attitute and is well liked and respected by his peers and club members.", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Stephen Cleary", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Consultant I Chief Marketing Officer | Brand Strategy | Digital Transformation | Marketing Strategies | Customer Insights & Experience", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephen-cleary-25aa164/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADcsuYBHrPmbIhv9Wd7-tYydg1XenmIFSE", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "John P. worked with Stephen but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "April 7, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "i worked together with stephen on the Indonesian Open in Bali in 2009 and found him to be one of the best golf professionals i have ever worked with. he ran the entire tournanment in coordination with the European PGA and from my hospitality angle i saw nothing short of excellence. This was the first time that the new Kuta Golf club had hosted this event and considering the short notice and the newness in the position he was a star and a joy to work with. Myself and my team did all of the catering for the VIP tents and Stephen and his staff were more then supportive. I reccomend Stephen to any excellence driven golf management organization who is looking for a flexible and hard working professional.", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "John P. Rees ", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Senior Vice President Hotel Operations Hard Rock International Passionate Hospitality Professional, Global Citizen, Restless Adventurer, Committed family supporter and ultimate disrupter", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/john-p-rees-40a3702/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABovUoBRQVOOVbtow4BPF_HnQZGF7xOnn4", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Vincent worked with Stephen but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "March 12, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "Stephen Banks bring to the table his passion, drive, enthusiasm and knowledge when I had the privilege of working with him during the prestigious Enjoy Jakarta Indonesian Open golf 2009 at the New Kuta Golf & Ocean View. He was the club General Manager then and was instrumental in leading his team of 200 strong to great success in hosting the event. Pleasant to work with, completely trustworthy and competent in his duties from pre event planning to completion of the tournament. His friendly and approchable nature won the respect of the tournament official from European and Asian Tours as well as the event promoter. Everyday no matter how difficult the one before, he would start afresh and positively which was crucial in producing a congenial and cooperative working environment.", "recommendationsReceived/10/name": "Vincent Brian Wong", "recommendationsReceived/10/subtitle": "Consultant at vbw Marketing", "recommendationsReceived/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-brian-wong-99415217/", "recommendationsReceived/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANnJAAB923Y-v6oMpJFZsVoXUTQoQDVudo", "recommendationsReceived/11/context": "Neil was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/11/date": "February 11, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/11/description": "Stephen organised 2 golf events on my behalf at Tam Dao during 2007. One was work related and the other was on behalf of the British Business Group in Vietnam for which I was Chairman for at that time. \n\nThe group sizes ranged from 150 to 180 people at each event. The events consisted of a days golfing and evening social functions with prize giving ceremonies. Both days went without a hitch and I was extremely impressed by the quality of the services that we were given\n\nStephen was extremely active in ensuring that both days were a great success  \n\nI have no hesitation in recommending Stephen as his work is of the highest standard.", "recommendationsReceived/11/name": "Neil Harvey", "recommendationsReceived/11/subtitle": "Director", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/neil-harvey-85ba3813/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALSlccBRUTbhhIRYydcL8-GKP-VAv7qHZU", "recommendationsReceived/12/context": "Mark worked with Stephen but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "February 4, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "Stephen took on Tam Dao Golf Resort and transformed it to one of the best golf courses in Vietnam. His strengths are forging excellent relationships with membership, creating a positive spirit among staff and organizing flawless golf events He's a positive, hands-on manager who brings a total commitment to his job.", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Mark Pierce", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "Senior Non-Profit Leader", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marktpierce/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAH8OXcBILBk5KW4_C2D7CAN-poXM6a8fGE", "recommendationsReceived/13/context": "Ken was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "January 21, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "Stephen is one of Golf's true professionals in every sence of the word . His on course skills make him an outstanding Club Professional , and his outstanding business and people management skills ensure great customer service while ensure shareholder profits grow at the club he is managing .", "recommendationsReceived/13/name": "Ken Newell", "recommendationsReceived/13/subtitle": "President Pepsico Beverages , China", "recommendationsReceived/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ken-newell-5341b42/", "recommendationsReceived/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABihPgB1UPVW-zaDdWxRPDDrTdm7QMyOzE", "recommendationsReceived/14/context": "Mark was Stephen's client", "recommendationsReceived/14/date": "January 11, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/14/description": "I was fortunate to have witnessed Stephen's work as Master of Ceremonies for t